    "steam_appid": 3317170,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/f24f57117538b428b28694df42e9a455.poster.avif?t=1771871683\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/f24f57117538b428b28694df42e9a455.webm?t=1771871683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>双影潜伏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款获奖同屏游戏《霓虹飞刃》中，融入人群，不动声色，追猎对手。此刻，你既是猎手，亦是猎物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/b5441a0fd857d7ac8b0657d5dfaa405a.poster.avif?t=1771871683\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/b5441a0fd857d7ac8b0657d5dfaa405a.webm?t=1771871683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/b5441a0fd857d7ac8b0657d5dfaa405a.mp4?t=1771871683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>诡谲战场</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每张地图都暗藏玄机。你可隐身林间、借风滚草制造骚动，或藏匿于悠然漫步的巨蜗牛身后。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/c78a92104edb7e139e49c50c05433b80.poster.avif?t=1771871683\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/c78a92104edb7e139e49c50c05433b80.webm?t=1771871683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/c78a92104edb7e139e49c50c05433b80.mp4?t=1771871683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自定战法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >潜行暗杀、设饵诱敌、格杀勿论，甚至偷窥对手操作——每种风格都将在人群中播下混乱与猜疑的种子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/5bc5bd6892828949cfbf24fda584b108.poster.avif?t=1771871683\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/5bc5bd6892828949cfbf24fda584b108.webm?t=1771871683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/5bc5bd6892828949cfbf24fda584b108.mp4?t=1771871683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>双人同控</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与好友共享一个手柄或键盘，上演面对面的终极对决。亦支持双控制器操作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/ed68020b3ec2b5c2609f56f2aef14a32.avif?t=1771871683\" alt=\"\"data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras_big/ed68020b3ec2b5c2609f56f2aef14a32.webp?t=1771871683 width=1560 height=755 /></span></p>",
